		<title>当季水果一览表合集（一口气看完全年应季水果时间表+水果属性+水果清洗规范）</title>
		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/4369.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 15 Jul 2023 10:45:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[果蔬知识]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[应季]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[水果]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[热性]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=4369</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[#挑战30天在头条写日记#1-12月应季水果时间表 1. 总表 3-5 6-8 9-11 12-2 记得吃应季 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><a style="color: red;">#挑战30天在头条写日记#</a>1-12月应季水果时间表</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">1.</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/9b5aa314b73c27faeac79d1c6f1d6a3a.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">总表</p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/8910c7d898b346d6c83f7c5257ec20b3.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">3-5</p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/c6a6f9c7ab03eb5539eb338ab605dbc1.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">6-8</p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/a8007331a74ca26754a78d3b868113ba.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">9-11</p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/0bd3ffb34079abb99f1825445a45e97a.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">12-2</p>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">记得吃应季水果会更营养健康哦！今天你吃对水果了吗？</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2.水果属性分类表大全</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/771e1c0ddad94785e7638410127234cb.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">水果除了热量还有属性和功效之分</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">寒性水果指的是热量密度低、富含纤维，但脂肪、糖分少的水果，有助于清火、解毒，适合热性体质者食用</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/64034f4ee741beefa9c99f0a50974283.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">凉性水果指的是性寒的水果，可以缓解燥热，夏季成熟的水果大部分是寒凉性的，适合一般体质食用</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/58e03ad51d46e300f28f664b921a20ed.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">热性水果指的是具有温热性质的水果，其可以补虚寒，如果在夏季手脚还觉得冰冷的话可以选择多吃热性水果</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/1b13bb63753e0a6ec4285a726566e176.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">温性水果指的是一类水果的统称，比如苹果、</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/84e95b5ea3f4745599248eee7e9af318.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">金桔、红毛丹等，适合寒性体质，可以祛寒补虚，促进人体能量代谢。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">平性水果是相对于寒凉和温热性质而言的一类水果，寒热性质不明显，较为平和，可调理脾胃，补充营养。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/1284cba39dd15af4ec454582963a20d7.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">可以根据自身体质选择适合自己的水果哦，比如女生生理期就要减少寒凉性水果摄入，体寒就可以通过补充温热性水果暖暖身，这样才能更好的发挥出水果应有的养生作用。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">3.水果清洗规范大全</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">清洗方法和技巧</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/8e2363f1172882977f76979df16a335b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/f191a25c5334f8bb4172e4e962a45f70.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/d0d460a38302db31fe24c0477fa1fcbd.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/6dca23bc8a491a0bce3f006b87507883.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/e1cb00bf005e6ce78895b45234e95823.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">请点赞收藏转发！</p>


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
